title: Digital Image Recovery
description:
A Very Handy Prog:
Digital Image Recovery
--------------------------------------------------------------

What is Digital Image Recovery?  
  
Digital Image Recovery is a data recovery tool for digital images.
The program is designed for media used by digital cameras. Common 
media types are:
  Flash Card(TM), SmartMedia (TM), SONY Memory Stick (TM), 
  IBM(TM) Micro Drive, Multimedia Card, Secure Digital Card 
  and Compact Disc.

The system requirements are:
* Memory card reader (the media has to be appear as a drive)
* Windows(R) 9X, ME, NT, 2000 or XP/Vista

How to use it.
1 Select the drive of your images.
2 Choose destination drive of the images to be recovered.
3 Press button Start.
